---
title: Pork and Wasabi Meatballs with Roasted Zucchini and Jasmine Rice
description: In this dish, juicy pork meatballs are baked to perfection. Served with ginger-infused rice and light and aromatic wasabi-mayo, this Japanese inspired meal is an ideal weeknight supper!
